,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f8c17f9420ee7c72cff3a8836a7dd76141f4cd","tid":413941,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"耶教唔係邪教咩而家"},{"pid":"ffc665896e4e512359a8773717e3a02b97815ac4","tid":413941,"uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">飛天義大利麵神教</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.knowing.asia/16c110c3-a0a3-4f10-8b89-11086a1a14e2/8466d07fea76f2077815a847ef4b4899.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.knowing.asia%2F16c110c3-a0a3-4f10-8b89-11086a1a14e2%2F8466d07fea76f2077815a847ef4b4899.png&h=a0b1cac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛行義大利麵怪物信仰的中心教義認為，一個不可見，且不可感知的「飛行著的意大利麵條怪物」在「一次嚴重的酗酒後」，創造了整個宇宙。據推測，正是酒精中毒導致飛行麵條怪創造的地球充滿種種瑕疵。所有支援演化論的證據都是麵條怪布置的。他通過讓事物顯得更古老，測試教徒的虔誠。當科學家採用放射測年法等科學方法以試圖確定事物年齡時，飛行麵條怪會通過「他麵條般神聖的附肢來改變測量結果」，以使結果顯得更古老。<br />\n<br />\n飛行義大利麵怪物信仰的天堂中有一座噴發啤酒的火山和一座脫衣舞場。地獄類似天堂，不同處在於火山噴出的是過期的啤酒（或馬尿）；脫衣舞娘都身患性病<br />\n<br />\nfrom WIKI</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夠竟要幾on9先會信</blockquote><br />\n講得出呢句都知你唔係好明呢個教嘅意義"},{"pid":"f82a811153c84b4cadec540d602bd32f5bced8a1","tid":413941,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">飛天義大利麵神教</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.knowing.asia/16c110c3-a0a3-4f10-8b89-11086a1a14e2/8466d07fea76f2077815a847ef4b4899.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.knowing.asia%2F16c110c3-a0a3-4f10-8b89-11086a1a14e2%2F8466d07fea76f2077815a847ef4b4899.png&h=a0b1cac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛行義大利麵怪物信仰的中心教義認為，一個不可見，且不可感知的「飛行著的意大利麵條怪物」在「一次嚴重的酗酒後」，創造了整個宇宙。據推測，正是酒精中毒導致飛行麵條怪創造的地球充滿種種瑕疵。所有支援演化論的證據都是麵條怪布置的。他通過讓事物顯得更古老，測試教徒的虔誠。當科學家採用放射測年法等科學方法以試圖確定事物年齡時，飛行麵條怪會通過「他麵條般神聖的附肢來改變測量結果」，以使結果顯得更古老。<br />\n<br />\n飛行義大利麵怪物信仰的天堂中有一座噴發啤酒的火山和一座脫衣舞場。地獄類似天堂，不同處在於火山噴出的是過期的啤酒（或馬尿）；脫衣舞娘都身患性病<br />\n<br />\nfrom WIKI</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夠竟要幾on9先會信</blockquote><br />\n講得出呢句都知你唔係好明呢個教嘅意義</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之後睇翻先知原來係諷刺其他宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前真係以為有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8607516277804b6206cd14fc3ec5b211e50de761","tid":413941,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f954b1b4c5c9f66a1be16e151afc913cd4e9c62a","tid":413941,"uid":138941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}